<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“百花公主骗了我！”妖怪说。他气得跺脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他叹了口气：“我不能生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31549</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我太爱她了。可是，那头猪跑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31550</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他会回到国王那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36772</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王会派军队来的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪想了一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43833</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，他有了一个计划。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49256</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他去了公主的房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52871</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“亲爱的。”妖怪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55461</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要去拜访你的父亲。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55462</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”百花公主震惊地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会告诉他我是个很好的人。”妖怪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以组成一个很幸福的家庭。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>公主还没来得及说话，妖怪就走出了房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我需要伪装一下。”他自言自语地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪迅速念了个咒。一道光闪过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪变成了一个英俊的年轻人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈！”他笑道。八戒跑回了宝象国。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107689</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他告诉国王他和悟净没能救回百花公主。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒低着头说：“我跑回来了。悟净被抓了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们必须救我的女儿。”国王说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118361</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他命令侍卫：“召集军队！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，一个信使跑了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126792</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“陛下，您的女婿来见您了。”信使说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135911</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王很疑惑：“我没有女婿啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个英俊的年轻人走进了大殿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您好，岳父。很抱歉，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145738</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我直到现在才来拜访您。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145739</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148880</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是谁？”国王问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148881</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156145</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“13年前，我和百花公主成了亲。”年轻人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156146</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在一片树林里发现了她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当时，有只老虎正要袭击她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165494</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我赶走了老虎，救了她。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165495</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王放松了一点，说道：“你很勇敢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171305</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175072</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，我非常勇敢。”年轻人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175073</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，从那以后，老虎一直想报仇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不久前，它成了精。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186500</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，他把自己扮成了一个和尚。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>年轻人看向唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他指着唐僧说：“就是那个和尚！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195774</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么！”唐僧大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195775</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王皱起眉头说：“我不相信你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会证明的。”年轻人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207837</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他指着唐僧念了个咒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207838</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一道光闪过。每个人都大吃一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只老虎坐在唐僧的位置！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225128</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在马厩里，一个男孩儿正在给唐僧的马喂草。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225129</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229765</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“唐僧的事情，你听说了吗？”另一个男孩儿问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229766</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他实际上是只老虎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232007</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有个英俊的年轻人让他现出了原形。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！”第一个男孩儿说，“那只老虎现在在哪里？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246648</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他被关在了笼子里。”另一个男孩儿说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天晚上，八戒一个人坐在外面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，他听见了一个声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259225</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂！”那个声音说，“八戒！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒看了看四周。“谁在叫我？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看见马在墙的后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267931</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在说话！”八戒叫起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276604</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘘！”马说，“我们有麻烦了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276605</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280179</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个年轻人把唐僧变成了一只老虎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧现在被关在笼子里了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，我知道！”八戒叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这太糟糕了！师父现在成了老虎，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净又被妖怪抓了。”他叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295663</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300425</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在不能去西天了。我们还是回家吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300426</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马用力咬了一下八戒的腿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”八戒叫道，“你干吗咬我？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不能回家！”马说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个年轻人很可能是妖怪假扮的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们得打败他，把师父救出来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324004</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，怎么做啊？”八戒问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324005</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马想了一会儿：“你去找悟空。他可以帮我们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>330056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒摇摇头说：“他不会帮我们的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>